  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long can you survive in the hood? Hood Ninja is an intense, fast-paced third-person fighting game that throws you into the heart of a gritty neighborhood where survival is the only thing on your mind. The player will face different adversities and opportunities to stay alive in the streets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/648d7539d8be4dfcca3bbe73d44d2afc.poster.avif?t=1730302103\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/648d7539d8be4dfcca3bbe73d44d2afc.webm?t=1730302103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/648d7539d8be4dfcca3bbe73d44d2afc.mp4?t=1730302103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grab your Ninja Costume</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a formidable ninja-wanna-be against ruthless gang members led by a powerful leader with one goal in mind: your elimination. You will face different sort of enemies, some you will have to escape from, some will be taking advantages of you, and some bystanders you will receive kindness from in return for yours. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/1ba98f6646eb907b35f51a89d501f74a.poster.avif?t=1730302103\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/1ba98f6646eb907b35f51a89d501f74a.webm?t=1730302103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/1ba98f6646eb907b35f51a89d501f74a.mp4?t=1730302103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How long can you survive in the hood? Hood Ninja is an intense, fast-paced third-person fighting game that throws you into the heart of a gritty neighborhood where survival is the only thing on your mind. The player will face different adversities and opportunities to stay alive in the streets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/648d7539d8be4dfcca3bbe73d44d2afc.poster.avif?t=1730302103\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/648d7539d8be4dfcca3bbe73d44d2afc.webm?t=1730302103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/648d7539d8be4dfcca3bbe73d44d2afc.mp4?t=1730302103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grab your Ninja Costume</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a formidable ninja-wanna-be against ruthless gang members led by a powerful leader with one goal in mind: your elimination. You will face different sort of enemies, some you will have to escape from, some will be taking advantages of you, and some bystanders you will receive kindness from in return for yours. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/1ba98f6646eb907b35f51a89d501f74a.poster.avif?t=1730302103\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/1ba98f6646eb907b35f51a89d501f74a.webm?t=1730302103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2801750/extras/1ba98f6646eb907b35f51a89d501f74a.mp4?t=1730302103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
